('w_family_A1_32','kind','/kaɪnd/','adjective','친절한, 다정한','Friendly and generous; thinking about others'' feelings.','She is always {kind} to the younger children.','그녀는 어린아이들에게 항상 친절해요.','kind','A1','family',1,'kind person helping smiling warm'),
