('w_family_A2_05','divorce','/dɪˈvɔːrs/','noun','이혼','The legal ending of a marriage.','Going through a {divorce} is difficult for children.','이혼 과정은 아이들에게 힘든 일이에요.','divorce','A2','family',1,'divorce separation legal documents sad'),
