('w_family_A2_07','partner','/ˈpɑːrtnər/','noun','파트너, 배우자','A person you are in a romantic relationship with.','Her {partner} supported her decision to go back to school.','그녀의 파트너는 그녀가 학교로 돌아가는 결정을 지지했어요.','partner','A2','family',1,'partners couple support teamwork together'),
('w_family_A2_08','teenager','/ˈtiːneɪdʒər/','noun','십대 청소년','A young person between the ages of 13 and 19.','Every {teenager} needs space to grow and make mistakes.','모든 십대 청소년은 성장하고 실수할 공간이 필요해요.','teenager','A2','family',1,'teenager youth school backpack outdoor'),
('w_family_A2_09','adult','/ˈædʌlt/','noun','성인','A person who is fully grown and legally an adult.','As an {adult}, she learned to manage her own finances.','성인이 된 후, 그녀는 스스로 재정을 관리하는 법을 배웠어요.','adult','A2','family',1,'adult independent confident city portrait'),
('w_family_A2_10','childhood','/ˈtʃaɪldhʊd/','noun','어린 시절, 유년기','The time when you are a child.','She has fond memories of her {childhood} in the countryside.','그녀는 시골에서의 어린 시절을 행복하게 기억해요.','childhood','A2','family',1,'childhood memories playing outdoor summer happy'),
('w_family_A2_11','raise','/reɪz/','verb','키우다, 양육하다','To look after a child until they are fully grown.','Her grandparents {raised} her after her parents passed away.','부모님이 돌아가신 후 할머니 할아버지가 그녀를 키워주셨어요.','raise','A2','family',1,'raising child family care nurture outdoor'),
('w_family_A2_12','support','/səˈpɔːrt/','verb','지지하다, 지원하다','To give help, encouragement, or money to someone.','His parents always {supported} his dream to become a musician.','그의 부모님은 항상 그가 음악가가 되려는 꿈을 지지해 주셨어요.','support','A2','family',1,'support family encouragement helping hands together'),
('w_family_A2_13','close','/kloʊs/','adjective','가까운, 친밀한','Having a strong relationship with someone.','She is very {close} to her younger sister.','그녀는 여동생과 매우 가까워요.','close','A2','family',1,'close siblings sisters smiling bond'),
('w_family_A2_14','nephew','/ˈnefjuː/','noun','조카 (남자)','A son of your brother or sister.','Her {nephew} is the same age as her own son.','그녀의 조카와 그녀의 아들은 나이가 같아요.','nephew','A2','family',1,'nephew aunt uncle family child playing'),
